{{#var:effects_formatted}}

## Notes

* '''''BENEFIT:''''' +2 [Penetration](/penetration/) against damaged targets from your Stiletto attacks. While most worn armor counters piercing damage, this modal should be useful for rapidly steady damage. You need high Penetration yourself and armor reduction (AR) against your opponent to see this succeed well.
* '''''PENALTY:''''' +50% Recovery time after your Stiletto attack.
